name: Nightfall
description:
Seven witches waiting when bleak death is near in silent grace
Conjuring the damned while opening the gates of Hell
Goddess, as your raging hand shall strike your spear and pierce the land
Accept my sacrifice and take my soul to realms beyond
Nightfall
Reap, oh great Death, with your fleshless womb
When night falls again, so falls the world
See them run from your eyeless skull
Nightfall
Cloak their hearts, let them fear the night
When life fade, the abyss will thrive
For when she rise, there's no turning back
